  body.ids
    block header
      include /partials/header
    

  .ids__wrapper.safety-page
    .ids__stack.XS
    h1 Ride safe
    .ids__text
      p Superpedestrian champions safe streets for everyone. We’re working toward a future where riders, pedestrians, bicyclists, transit users, people with disabilities, and drivers share safe streets!
    
    
    .ids__grid.XS
      .ids__grid-cell
        a(href="#safe-riders") Safe riders
      .ids__grid-cell
        a(href="#safe-streets") Safe streets
      .ids__grid-cell
        a(href="#safe-vehicles") Safe vehicles
      .ids__grid-cell
        a(href="#safe-partners") Safety partners 
    
    
    .ids__stack.M
    h3#safe-riders Safe riders
    .ids__stack.XS
    .ids__text
      p Superpedestrian’s technology is 
        a(href="/vehicles") designed 
      p to keep you safe. But how you ride them matters just as much.
    .ids__stack.XS
    .ids__grid
      .ids__grid-cell
        p Be smart, be safe:
        ul
          li Always wear a helmet
          li Only one person per vehicle
          li Never ride under the influence
          li You must be 18+ to ride
      .ids__grid-cell
        img(src="/images/girl-helmet.jpeg", alt="girl with helmet")
    
    .ids__stack.M
    .ids__text
      h4 No helmet? We've got you covered
      .ids__grid.XS
      .ids__text
        p We always recommend that you wear a helmet. That’s why we’ve teamed up with our favorite brands to offer helmets to our riders at an affordable price. 
      .ids__grid.XS
    .ids__grid
      .ids__grid-cell
        ul  
          li BERN offers discounted helmets to LINK riders in the USA. Purchase any helmet on the 
            a(href="https://www.bernhelmets.com/collections/bike")  Bern website
            p and enter code LINKxBERN25 at checkout for 25% off.
          .ids__grid.XS
          li CLOSCA offers discounted helmets to LINK riders across Europe, and the Middle East*.
            p Purchase either the 
              a(href="https://closca.com/products/closca-helmet-loop")  Helmet Loop
            p or 
              a(href="https://closca.com/products/closca-helmet-loop-reflective")  Helmet Loop Reflective 
            p via the Closca website and enter code CLOSCAxLINK15 at checkout for 15% off.
          .ids__grid.XS
          li HELMET GIVEAWAYS. We give away free helmets at many community events. We’ve given thousands of free helmets to riders so far, and we’re just getting started.


    .ids__stack.M
    #safe-streets
      h3 Safe Streets
      .ids__stack.XS
      .ids__text
        p Superpedestrian riders know that safety comes first. These are the principles we teach in our Level Up safety trainings.
      .ids__stack.XS
      .ids__grid
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/two-person.jpeg", alt="two-person")
        .ids__grid-cell
          p Rules of the road:
          ul
            li Follow traffic laws and street signs
            li Always let pedestrians go first
            li Ride in the bike lane when available
            li Ride with traffic on one-way streets
          p See your local page for city-specific rules
    
    .ids__stack.M
    
    .ids__grid#safe-parking
      .ids__grid-cell
        ul Parking guidelines:
        .ids__stack.XS 
          li Use the kickstand to park upright
          .ids__stack.XS
          li Keep walkways clear
          .ids__stack.XS
          li Don’t block curb cuts, access ramps, doors, or loading docks
          .ids__stack.XS
          li Keep bus stops clear
          .ids__stack.XS 
          p You must park safely and courteously. In most cities, you are required to take a photo showing proper parking. 
      .ids__grid-cell
        img(src="/images/parking.jpeg", alt="parking")

    .ids__stack.M

    .ids__text
      .ids__grid-cell
        ul Vision Zero
          .ids__stack.XS
          p We firmly believe in the core principles of 
            a(href="http://www.towardszerofoundation.org/thesafesystem/")   Vision Zero
            p – that no one should be killed or seriously injured on our roads, and that thoughtful city planning and engineering hold the most power to prevent crashes. We’re doing our part to make Vision Zero a reality: 
          li Our technology quickly enforces slow-ride and no-ride zones to detect and prevent unsafe riding
          li We 
            a(href="https://la.streetsblog.org/2021/09/07/sunset4all-celebrates-achieving-crowdfunding-milestone/")   advocate for and invest in 
            p smart street designs
          li We host and sponsor safe riding education events and workshops
          li We partner with 
            a(href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1bUwTXyP_17C7APwqU36XqS65rZCs9vz1zAMOuFGXwT0/edit#heading=h.yhn91hgjqn2b")   organizations 
            p that are also dedicated to Vision Zero work
        .ids__stack.M
    
    

    h3#safe-vehicles Safe Vehicles
    .ids__stack.XS
    p We design, manufacture, and operate our scooters with safety as our #1 priority. We test our scooters so they perform 2-4x better than others when handling challenges like bumps or hard braking.
    .ids__stack.XS
    a.ids__button-link(href="/vacancies/safety") Our vehicles
    .ids__stack.S
    .ids__grid
      .ids__grid-cell
        p Our scooters are built better: 
        ul
          li Three (3) independent brakes 
          li Wider and longer deck for stability
          li High-visibility colors, lights, and reflectors
          li Long-range battery (61 mi / 98 km)
          li Steel reinforced frame to withstand bumps
          li Tip-over detection
          a.ids__button-link(href="/vacancies/safety") Our technology
      .ids__grid-cell
        img(src="/images/engineer.jpeg", alt="engineer")
        .ids__stack.S

    .ids__stack.M 

    #safe-partners
      h3 Safe Partners
      .ids__stack.XS
      p We design, manufacture, and operate our scooters with safety as our #1 priority. We test our scooters so they perform 2-4x better than others when handling challenges like bumps or hard braking.
      .ids__stack.XS
      .ids__grid.L
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner1.png", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner2.jpeg", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner3.png", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner4.png", alt="partner")

      .ids__grid.L
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner5.png", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner6.jpeg", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner7.jpeg", alt="partner")
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner8.jpeg", alt="partner")
      
      .ids__grid.L
        .ids__grid-cell
          img(src="/images/partner9.png", alt="partner")   
      


  
  .ids__stack.M
